#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; is, well, a jukebox. As is typical with many jukebox applications, "
"&juk; allows you to edit the <quote>tags</quote> of your audio files, and "
"manage your collection and playlists."
msgstr ""
"&juk; je, no, jukebox. Kot je značilno za mnoge aplikacije jukebox, vam "
"&juk; omogoča urejanje <quote>oznak</quote> vaših zvočnih datotek ter "
"upravljanje vaše zbirke in seznamov predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &juk;"
msgstr "Uporaba &juk;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &juk;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &juk;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &juk; in action."
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona &juk; v akciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; maintains a list of all files that it knows about. This is called the "
"<guilabel>Collection List</guilabel>. The collection list is specific to "
"&juk; and is not shared with other applications."
msgstr ""
"&juk; vzdržuje seznam vseh datotek, za katere ve. To se imenuje "
"<guilabel>Seznam zbirk</guilabel>. Seznam zbirk je specifičen za &juk; in ni "
"v skupni rabi z drugimi aplikacijami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Independent of the Collection List, are playlists. You can have as many "
"playlists as you want. You can use &juk; created playlists with other media "
"players (such as &amarok; or <application>xmms</application>) and you can "
"manage playlists created in those applications from within &juk;."
msgstr ""
"Seznami predvajanja so neodvisni od seznama zbirk. Imate lahko toliko "
"seznamov predvajanja, kot želite. Uporabite lahko ustvarjene sezname "
"predvajanja z drugimi predstavnostnimi predvajalniki (kot je &amarok; ali "
"<application>xmms</application>) uporabi &juk; in lahko upravljate sezname "
"predvajanja, ustvarjene v teh aplikacijah znotraj &juk;a."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add files to the Collection List individually, using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and selecting them from a standard &kde; file dialog. You can "
"add entire folders using <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Folders "
"added this way will be rescanned every time you start &juk;. You can even "
"define folders inside these folders that will be excluded from scan. You can "
"force the folders to be rescanned by right-clicking on the "
"<guilabel>Collection List</guilabel> icon, and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke lahko dodate na seznam zbirk posamezno, tako da uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in jih izberete v standardnem oknu &kde; pogovorno okno "
"datoteke. Celotne mape lahko dodate z <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje map...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Tako "
"dodane mape bodo ponovno pregledane vsakič, ko zaženete &juk;. V teh mapah "
"lahko celo določite mape, ki bodo izključene iz pregleda. Mapam lahko "
"vsilite v ponovno skeniranje tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete ikono "
"<guilabel>Seznam zbirk</guilabel> in izberete <guimenuitem>Znova naloži</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding a song to a playlist will automatically add its file to the "
"Collection List, but adding a file to the Collection List won't "
"automatically add the song to any playlists."
msgstr ""
"Če pesem dodate na seznam predvajanja, bo njena datoteka samodejno dodana na "
"seznam zbirk, vendar dodajanje datoteke na seznam zbirk ne bo samodejno "
"dodalo skladbe na noben seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can quickly create a playlist from your entire Collection List, by &RMB; "
"clicking on the <guilabel>Collection List</guilabel> icon, and choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate</guimenuitem>. The resulting playlist is a normal "
"playlist, and editing it will not affect the <guilabel>Collection List</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Seznam predvajanja lahko hitro ustvarite iz celotnega seznama zbirk z &RMB; "
"s klikom na ikono <guilabel>Seznam zbirk</guilabel> in izbiro "
"<guimenuitem>Podvoji</guimenuitem>. Nastali seznam predvajanja je običajen "
"seznam predvajanja in njegovo urejanje ne bo vplivalo na <guilabel>Seznam "
"zbirk</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add playlist files created outside &juk; individually by selecting "
"them with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Any playlist files found in folders you add with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> will also be added automatically."
msgstr ""
"Dodate lahko datoteke s seznami predvajanja, ustvarjene zunaj &juk; "
"posamezno tako, da jih izberete z <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vse datoteke "
"seznama predvajanja, ki jih najdete v mapah, ki jih dodate z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje map...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, bodo prav tako dodane samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a new empty playlist, a search playlist or a playlist from a "
"folder by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> or the <guiicon>New</guiicon> icon on the toolbar. "
"You will be prompted for a name, and then an icon for that playlist will "
"appear in the playlist pane. You can now drag and drop files from the "
"Collection List, or from other playlists, to your playlist. Use the "
"<guiicon>Save</guiicon> icon or <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to save the playlist at "
"any time."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite lahko nov prazen seznam predvajanja, iskalni seznam predvajanja "
"ali seznam predvajanja iz mape, tako da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> ali <guiicon>Novo</guiicon> v orodni vrstici. Pozvani boste k "
"vnosu imena, nato pa se bo v podoknu seznama predvajanja prikazala ikona za "
"ta seznam predvajanja. Zdaj lahko povlečete in spustite datoteke s seznama "
"zbirke ali drugih seznamov predvajanja na svoj seznam predvajanja. Uporabite "
"ikono <guiicon>Shrani</guiicon> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da kadar koli "
"shranite seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Song List"
msgstr "Seznam pesmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are viewing the Collection List, the main pane contains all the "
"files that &juk; knows about. When you are viewing a playlist, only the "
"songs that are in that playlist are shown. In either case, the appearance "
"and behavior of the list is the same."
msgstr ""
"Ko si ogledujete seznam zbirk, so v glavnem podoknu vse datoteke, ki jih "
"&juk; pozna. Ko si ogledujete seznam predvajanja, so prikazane samo pesmi, "
"ki so na tem seznamu predvajanja. V obeh primerih sta videz in obnašanje "
"seznama enaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each song takes one row in the display. There is a column for each metadata "
"field that &juk; tracks. These columns correspond to the fields available to "
"edit in the tag editor."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka skladba ima eno vrstico na zaslonu. Obstaja stolpec za vsako "
"metapodatkovno polje, ki ga &juk; sledi. Ti stolpci ustrezajo poljem, ki so "
"na voljo za urejanje v urejevalniku oznak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reorder the list at any time by &LMB; clicking on the column header. "
"This will first sort the files in ascending order based on the contents of "
"that column. If you &LMB; click again on the same header, the files will be "
"re-sorted in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Seznam lahko kadar koli preuredite z &LMB; s klikom na glavo stolpca. To bo "
"najprej razvrstilo datoteke v naraščajočem vrstnem redu glede na vsebino "
"tega stolpca. Če &LMB; znova kliknite na isto glavo, bodo datoteke ponovno "
"razvrščene v padajočem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The columns are initially sized wide enough to show the longest entry "
"available. You can resize the columns by placing your mouse cursor on the "
"divider between two columns. When the cursor changes from a pointer, &LMB; "
"click and drag in the direction you want to resize the columns."
msgstr ""
"Stolpci so na začetku dovolj široki, da prikažejo najdaljši vnos, ki je na "
"voljo. Velikost stolpcev lahko spremenite tako, da kazalec miške postavite "
"na ločnico med dvema stolpcema. Ko se kazalec spremeni iz kazalca, &LMB; "
"kliknite in povlecite v smeri, v kateri želite spremeniti velikost stolpcev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reorder the columns by &LMB; clicking on a header and dragging the "
"header to the left or right. You cannot drag past the edge of the window "
"when doing this however, so you may need to scroll a little to the left or "
"right, and repeat dragging the header, until you have placed it in your "
"preferred position."
msgstr ""
"Stolpce lahko preuredite z &LMB; klik na glavo in vlečenje glave v levo ali "
"desno. Vendar pri tem ne morete povleči mimo roba okna, zato se boste morda "
"morali pomakniti nekoliko v levo ali desno in ponavljati vlečenje glave, "
"dokler je ne postavite na želeno mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can hide or unhide columns by &RMB; clicking on a column header, and "
"clicking on the name of the column to change."
msgstr ""
"Stolpce lahko skrijete ali razkrijete z &RMB; klik na glavo stolpca in klik "
"na ime stolpca za spremembo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LMB; double clicking on a file will play it with the built-in player. If "
"another song was already playing, it will stop, and the new song will play."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; dvojni klik na datoteko jo bo predvajal z vgrajenim predvajalnikom. Če "
"se je že predvajala druga pesem, se bo ustavila in predvajala se bo nova "
"pesem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "&RMB; clicking on a file offers you several options:"
msgstr "&RMB; s klikom na datoteko se vam ponudi več možnosti:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Play Queue"
msgstr "Dodaj v čakalno vrsto za predvajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will start playing the file as soon as the current song is over. If no "
"song is playing, the file will be played when you next hit the "
"<guiicon>Play</guiicon> button. If you have already chosen the "
"<guimenuitem>Add to Play Queue</guimenuitem> option on a different file, "
"then this file will override that selection."
msgstr ""
"To bo začelo predvajanje datoteke takoj, ko bo trenutna skladba končana. Če "
"se ne predvaja nobena pesem, bo datoteka predvajana, ko naslednjič "
"pritisnete gumb <guiicon>Predvajaj</guiicon>. Če ste že izbrali možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj v čakalno vrsto za predvajanje</guimenuitem> za drugo "
"datoteko, bo ta datoteka preglasila to izbiro."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>...</para>"
msgstr "<para>...</para>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove from Playlist"
msgstr "Odstrani s seznama predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are viewing the Collection List, choosing this action will remove the "
"file from the list, and will also remove all corresponding entries for this "
"song from all playlists. You should note that if this file is in a folder "
"that &juk; scans on startup, it will be readded to the Collection List the "
"next time you start up &juk; but it won't be automatically added to any "
"playlists."
msgstr ""
"Če si ogledujete seznam zbirk, boste z izbiro tega dejanja odstranili "
"datoteko s seznama in odstranili tudi vse ustrezne vnose za to pesem z vseh "
"seznamov predvajanja. Upoštevajte, da če je ta datoteka v mapi, ki jo &juk; "
"prečeše ob zagonu, bo prebran na seznam zbirk, ko naslednjič zaženete &juk; "
"vendar ne bo samodejno dodan nobenemu seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are viewing a playlist, <guimenuitem>Remove from Playlist</"
"guimenuitem> will simply remove the song from the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Če si ogledujete seznam predvajanja, bo <guimenuitem>Odstrani s seznama "
"predvajanja</guimenuitem> pesem preprosto odstranil s seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit <replaceable>Column Title</replaceable>"
msgstr "Uredi <replaceable>Naslov stolpca</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will allow you to edit the currently highlighted song, in the column you "
"clicked in. For example, if you do not have the tag editor visible, and you "
"are busy creating a playlist, but you notice a mis-spelling in an artist "
"name, you can edit it directly with this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Omogočil vam bo urejanje trenutno označene skladbe v stolpcu, v katerem ste "
"kliknili. Če na primer nimate vidnega urejevalnika oznak in ste zaposleni z "
"ustvarjanjem seznama predvajanja, vendar opazite napačno črkovanje v imenu "
"izvajalca, lahko ga urejate neposredno s to postavko menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes made in this manner are always saved immediately as soon as you "
"click elsewhere and are finished editing."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe, narejene na ta način, se vedno shranijo takoj, ko kliknete drugje "
"in končate urejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item will be disabled if &juk; detects that the track you have "
"selected is read-only."
msgstr ""
"Ta element menija bo onemogočen, če &juk; zazna, da je skladba, ki ste jo "
"izbrali, samo za branje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Refresh"
msgstr "Osveži"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will reload the tag information of the selected files, in case the "
"files have been changed while &juk; was running."
msgstr ""
"To bo znova naložilo informacije o oznaki izbranih datotek, če so bile "
"datoteke spremenjene medtem ko je &juk; tekel."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will remove the file from the Collection List, remove all entries for "
"the song in all playlists, and delete the file from your disk. You cannot "
"undo this, although you will be asked to confirm your choice. Use this with "
"caution."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste odstranili datoteko s seznama zbirke, odstranili vse vnose za "
"pesem na vseh seznamih predvajanja in izbrisali datoteko z diska. Tega ne "
"morete razveljaviti, vendar boste morali potrditi svojo izbiro. To "
"uporabljajte previdno."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Guess Tag Information"
msgstr "Informacije o oznaki Ugani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will make &juk; try to guess information such as the Artist and Title "
"of a song. &juk; employs different methods of guessing:"
msgstr ""
"S tem bo &juk; poskusite uganiti podatke, kot sta izvajalec in naslov pesmi. "
"&juk; uporablja različne metode ugibanja:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "From File Name"
msgstr "Iz imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try to guess the tags of the song based on its filename. For "
"example, a song name such as <filename>Roxette - You've Got the Look.mp3</"
"filename> would guess Roxette for the artist and You've Got the Look as the "
"title. You can adjust the way &juk; guesses for tags by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings </guimenu><guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which will open the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-"
"guesser-configuration\">Tag Guesser dialog</link>. &juk; will not replace "
"tags that it did not guess from the file name."
msgstr ""
"&juk; bo poskušal uganiti oznake pesmi na podlagi imena datoteke. Na primer, "
"ime pesmi, kot je <filename>Roxette - You've Got the Look.mp3</filename>, bi "
"uganilo Roxette kot izvajalca in You've Got the Look kot naslov. Prilagodite "
"lahko način &juk; ugiba za oznake tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve </guimenu><guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kar odpre <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-"
"configuration\" >Pogovorno okno Uganjevalnik oznak</link>. &juk; ne bo "
"zamenjal oznak, ki jih ni uganil iz imena datoteke."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "From Internet"
msgstr "Iz interneta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try to guess the tags of the song by using the MusicBrainz "
"program. You must have MusicBrainz installed for this command to work."
msgstr ""
"&juk; bo poskušal uganiti oznake pesmi s pomočjo programa MusicBrainz. Da ta "
"ukaz deluje, morate imeti nameščen MusicBrainz."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename File"
msgstr "Preimenuj datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will rename the selected files to conform to a given format. You must "
"choose the way you want the files renamed first by selecting <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Renamer...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. The resulting name of each file is based on its metadata tags. "
"For example, the Ogg Vorbis song <quote>The Theme (Metroid)</quote> by "
"Stemage could result in <filename>/usr/share/music/Stemage/The Theme "
"(Metroid).ogg</filename>."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste preimenovali izbrane datoteke, da bodo ustrezale danemu formatu. "
"Najprej morate izbrati način preimenovanja datotek, tako da izberete "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenovalnik "
"datotek...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Končno ime vsake datoteke temelji na "
"njenih metapodatkovnih oznakah. Na primer, pesem Ogg Vorbis <quote>The Theme "
"(Metroid)</quote> avtorja Stemage lahko najde <filename>/usr/share/music/"
"Stemage/The Theme (Metroid).ogg</filename>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create Playlist From Selected Items"
msgstr "Ustvari seznam predvajanja iz izbranih elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to quickly create a playlist from songs in your Collection "
"List. This function will prompt you for a name for the new playlist, and "
"will then insert all of the songs that are selected into the new playlist."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča hitro ustvarjanje seznama predvajanja iz skladb na vašem "
"Seznamu zbirke. Ta funkcija vas bo pozvala k vnosu imena za nov seznam "
"predvajanja in bo nato v nov seznam predvajanja vstavila vse izbrane pesmi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Selected Items to Audio or Data CD"
msgstr "Dodajte izbrane elemente na zvočni ali podatkovni CD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to quickly create a K3b &CD;-burning project from your "
"selected songs. &juk; will ask you if you would like an Audio &CD; project "
"or a Data &CD; project, unless K3b already has a project open."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča hitro ustvarjanje projekta za zapisovanje &CD; K3b iz vaših "
"izbranih pesmi. &juk; vas bo vprašal, ali želite Audio &CD; projekt ali Data "
"&CD; projekt, razen če ima K3b že odprt projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If K3b is not already running, &juk; will start it up for you. After that, "
"&juk; will add your selected files to the current K3b project. You can then "
"save the project in K3b for burning later, or burn the &CD; right away."
msgstr ""
"Če se K3b še ne izvaja, &juk; ga bo zagnal namesto vas. Po tem je &juk; bo "
"vaše izbrane datoteke dodal trenutnemu projektu K3b. Nato lahko projekt "
"shranite v K3b za kasnejši zapis ali zapišete &CD; takoj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "&juk; Playlists"
msgstr "&juk; Seznami predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A playlist is simply a collection of songs grouped by some category. For "
"example, you may have a playlist of songs that you listen to while coding, "
"while trying to sleep, or even when you need a laugh. &juk; supports several "
"different types of playlists."
msgstr ""
"Seznam predvajanja je preprosto zbirka skladb, razvrščenih po neki "
"kategoriji. Na primer, morda imate seznam skladb, ki jih poslušate med "
"kodiranjem, medtem ko poskušate spati ali celo, ko se morate nasmejati. "
"&juk; podpira več različnih vrst seznamov predvajanja."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal playlists"
msgstr "Običajni seznami predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most common kind of playlist. It is a playlist composed of "
"files, just like the Collection List."
msgstr ""
"To je najpogostejša vrsta seznama predvajanja. To je seznam predvajanja, "
"sestavljen iz datotek, tako kot seznam zbirke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "The history playlist"
msgstr "Seznam zgodovine predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this playlist (by enabling <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show History</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, this playlist "
"will record every song that &juk; plays. The playlist will have an extra "
"column, <guilabel>Time</guilabel>, which records the exact time and date the "
"song played. The playlist doesn't start tracking the history until it is "
"enabled, however."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite ta seznam predvajanja (če omogočite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži zgodovino</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, bo ta seznam predvajanja posnel vsako skladbo, ki "
"jo predvaja &juk;. Seznam predvajanja bo imel dodaten stolpec <guilabel>Čas</"
"guilabel>, ki beleži točen čas in datum predvajanja skladbe. Seznam "
"predvajanja pa ne začne slediti zgodovini, dokler ni omogočen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search playlists"
msgstr "Iskanje seznamov predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a playlist which is based off of a search. You can create a playlist "
"like this by clicking <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by "
"clicking on the <link linkend=\"juk-advanced-search-dialog\">Search "
"Playlist</link> button on the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam predvajanja, ki temelji na iskanju. Takšen seznam predvajanja "
"lahko ustvarite tako, da kliknete <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Išči seznam predvajanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali kliknete <link linkend =\"juk-advanced-search-"
"dialog\">Išči seznam predvajanja</link> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After creating this playlist, it will keep track of which songs in the "
"Collection List match your criteria, and automatically update itself "
"accordingly whenever the Collection List changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvari ta seznam predvajanja, bo spremljal, katere skladbe na seznamu "
"zbirk ustrezajo vašim kriterijem, in se samodejno ustrezno posodobil, ko se "
"bo seznam zbirk spremenil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playlists are organized in the <guilabel>Playlist pane</guilabel>, which is "
"the vertical bar at the left. In this pane is an icon for every playlist you "
"have. There are different view mode for this pane, which can be selected "
"from the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Seznami predvajanja so organizirani v <guilabel>podoknu seznama predvajanja</"
"guilabel>, ki je navpična vrstica na levi. V tem podoknu je ikona za vsak "
"seznam predvajanja, ki ga imate. Za to podokno obstajajo različni načini "
"pogleda, ki jih lahko izberete v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default View mode"
msgstr "Privzeti način pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default view mode. In this mode, all the playlists are shown as "
"large icons, one above the other in the view mode."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeti način pogleda. V tem načinu so vsi seznami predvajanja "
"prikazani kot velike ikone, ena nad drugo v načinu pogleda."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compact View mode"
msgstr "Način kompaktnega pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is similar to the Normal Viewmode, with the exception that the "
"playlists are represented with horizontal bars with small icons instead of "
"with square boxes."
msgstr ""
"Ta način je podoben običajnemu načinu pogleda, z izjemo, da so seznami "
"predvajanja predstavljeni z vodoravnimi črtami z majhnimi ikonami namesto s "
"kvadratnimi okvirji."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tree View mode"
msgstr "Način drevesnega pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is the most powerful. This mode is just like the Compact viewmode, "
"except that the Collection List is now the root of a tree of virtual "
"playlists. The Collection List has three children nodes, Artist, Album, and "
"Genre. Each of these node has children representing all of the entries from "
"that specific category. For example, if your Collection List contains music "
"from 4 different artists, you would have 4 entries under the artist node."
msgstr ""
"Ta način je najmočnejši. Ta način je podoben kompaktnemu načinu pogleda, le "
"da je seznam zbirk zdaj koren drevesa navideznih seznamov predvajanja. "
"Seznam zbirk ima tri podrejena vozlišča, Izvajalec, Album in Žanr. Vsako od "
"teh vozlišč ima podrejene osebe, ki predstavljajo vse vnose iz te posebne "
"kategorije. Na primer, če vaš seznam zbirk vsebuje glasbo 4 različnih "
"izvajalcev, bi imeli pod vozliščem izvajalca 4 vnose."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One nifty feature of the tree view mode is something called drag-and-drop "
"retagging. Simply select some files in the track list, and drag them onto "
"one of the artist, album, or genre nodes under Collection List. The songs "
"will automatically be retagged to match the item you dropped the tracks on. "
"For example, if you drag a group of tracks onto a Genre called \"Rock\", all "
"of the tracks will be retagged will a Genre tag of Rock."
msgstr ""
"Ena izvrstna funkcija načina drevesnega pogleda je nekaj, kar se imenuje "
"ponovno označevanje povleci in spusti. Preprosto izberite nekaj datotek na "
"seznamu skladb in jih povlecite na eno od vozlišč izvajalca, albuma ali "
"zvrsti pod seznamom zbirk. Pesmi bodo samodejno znova označene, da se bodo "
"ujemale z elementom, na katerega ste spustili skladbe. Če na primer "
"povlečete skupino skladb na žanr z imenom \"Rock\", bodo vse skladbe ponovno "
"označene z oznako žanra Rock."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &juk; Tag Editor"
msgstr "&juk; Urejevalnik oznak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For many file formats, it is practical to use the filename to describe the "
"contents of the file: <quote><filename>Report for the board - June 2003.doc</"
"filename></quote> for example, may be all the information you need in order "
"to find that file again. Trying to capture all the useful information about "
"a particular song however, could lead to filenames like this: "
"<quote><filename>Type O Negative - The Glorious Liberation Of The Peoples "
"Technocratic Republic Of Vinnland By The Combined Forces Of The United "
"Territories Of Europa.mp3</filename></quote> or <quote><filename>Various "
"Artists_15_The Smithsonian Collection of Classic Jazz Volume II_Jimmie "
"Lunceford &amp; His Orchestra - Organ Grinder's Swing.mp3</filename></"
"quote>. These are neither very practical to use, nor do they contain all of "
"the useful information that you might have collected about the song. Adding "
"the album, and track number, for example, to the first would make it even "
"longer and more unmanageable, while still not telling you at a glance the "
"year it was released, or what style of music it is, if you're not familiar "
"with the artist."
msgstr ""
"Pri mnogih formatih datotek je praktično uporabiti ime datoteke za opis "
"vsebine datoteke: <quote><filename>Poročilo za odbor - junij 2003.doc</"
"filename></quote>, na primer, lahko vse informacije, ki jih potrebujete za "
"ponovno iskanje te datoteke. Poskus zajeti vse uporabne informacije o "
"določeni pesmi pa bi lahko privedel do takih imen datotek: "
"<quote><filename>Type O Negative - The Glorious Liberation Of The Peoples "
"Technocratic Republic Of Vinnland By The Combined Forces Of the United "
"Territories Of Europa.mp3</filename></quote> ali <quote><filename>Various "
"Artists_15_The Smithsonian Collection of Classic Jazz Volume II_Jimmie "
"Lunceford &amp; His Orchestra - Organ Grinder's Swing.mp3</filename></"
"quote>. Ti niso niti zelo praktični za uporabo niti ne vsebujejo vseh "
"koristnih informacij, ki ste jih morda zbrali o pesmi. Če bi album in "
"številko skladbe na primer dodali prvemu, bi bil album še daljši in bolj "
"neobvladljiv, hkrati pa vam še vedno ne bi bilo jasno, v katerem letu je bil "
"izdan ali za kateri slog glasbe gre, če niste poznali umetnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The solution then, is to store this kind of metadata inside the files "
"themselves. Mp3 and ogg files can also contain small snippets of text which "
"you can use to describe the content of the file. There are several formats, "
"but &juk; hides the details of the differences between them, and provides a "
"standard way to edit a standard subset of well known tags for all your audio "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Rešitev je torej shranjevanje tovrstnih metapodatkov v same datoteke. "
"Datoteke mp3 in ogg lahko vsebujejo tudi majhne delčke besedila, ki jih "
"lahko uporabite za opis vsebine datoteke. Obstaja več formatov, vendar &juk; "
"skrije podrobnosti o razlikah med njimi in nudi standarden način za urejanje "
"standardne podnabora dobro znanih oznak za vse vaše zvočne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk;'s full featured tag editor allows you to edit the tags in both mp3 and "
"ogg files. You can edit single files or multiple files, and you can select a "
"mix of mp3 and ogg files to edit. The only requirement is that you have "
"write access to the files themselves; you cannot edit the tags of a file "
"that is mounted from a &CD-ROM; for example."
msgstr ""
"&juk;-jev urejevalnik oznak s polnimi funkcijami vam omogoča urejanje oznak "
"v datotekah mp3 in ogg. Urejate lahko posamezne datoteke ali več datotek in "
"izberete lahko mešanico datotek mp3 in ogg za urejanje. Edina zahteva je, da "
"imate dostop za pisanje do samih datotek; ne morete urejati oznak datoteke, "
"ki je nameščena iz &CD-ROM; na primer"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the Tags in a Single File"
msgstr "Urejanje oznak v eni datoteki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit the tag in a single file, select it in either the collection list or "
"any entries it has in any playlist. If the tag editor is not visible, enable "
"it by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag "
"Editor</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The tag editor displays in the bottom of "
"the list view."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti oznako v eni datoteki, jo izberite bodisi na seznamu zbirk "
"ali katere koli vnose, ki jih ima na katerem koli seznamu predvajanja. Če "
"urejevalnik oznak ni viden, ga omogočite tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži urejevalnik oznak</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Urejevalnik oznak se prikaže na dnu pogleda "
"seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply type into any of the editable fields to change the information. When "
"you are done, &LMB; click back in the list, and you will be prompted to save "
"your changes."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto vnesite v katero koli polje, ki ga je mogoče urejati, da "
"spremenite podatke. Ko končate, &LMB; kliknite nazaj na seznamu in pozvani "
"boste, da shranite spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find that the tag editor remains disabled when you've clicked on a "
"file. This happens when &juk; has detected that the track is read-only."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste ugotovili, da urejevalnik oznak ostane onemogočen, ko kliknete "
"datoteko. To se zgodi, ko &juk; je zaznal, da je skladba samo za branje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tag Editor Fields"
msgstr "Polja urejevalnika oznak"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Artist Name:"
msgstr "Ime izvajalca:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the Artist(s) who released the song."
msgstr "Ime izvajalca(-ev), ki je izdal pesem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track name:"
msgstr "Ime skladbe:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the song."
msgstr "Ime pesmi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Album name:"
msgstr "Ime albuma:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the album the song was released on."
msgstr "Ime albuma, na katerem je bila pesem izdana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Genre:"
msgstr "Žanr:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Style</quote> of the music. &juk; provides a list corresponding "
"roughly to the informal id3 standard, but you are free to type your own "
"entries in this list."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Slog</quote> glasbe. &juk; nudi seznam, ki približno ustreza "
"neformalnemu standardu id3, vendar lahko na ta seznam vnesete svoje vnose."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "File name:"
msgstr "Ime datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of the actual file on disk. You can edit this directly, and "
"when you save, the file will be renamed."
msgstr ""
"Ime dejanske datoteke na disku. To lahko urejate neposredno in ko shranite, "
"bo datoteka preimenovana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track:"
msgstr "Skladba:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "The position of the track on the original recording."
msgstr "Položaj skladbe na izvirnem posnetku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Year:"
msgstr "Leto:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "The year the song was released."
msgstr "Leto, ko je bila pesem izdana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length:"
msgstr "Dolžina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523 index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is not editable, it is simply shown for information."
msgstr "Tega ni mogoče urejati, prikazano je samo kot informacija."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bitrate:"
msgstr "Bitna hitrost:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment:"
msgstr "Komentar:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add your own free text comment here, with additional notes &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko dodate svoj komentar s prostim besedilom z dodatnimi opombami %etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:543 index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can explicitly and immediately save your changes at any time using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu entry or by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe lahko izrecno in takoj shranite kadar koli z menijskim vnosom "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali s pritiskom <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the Tags in Multiple Files"
msgstr "Urejanje oznak v več datotekah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select multiple files in the list view, and edit one or more fields "
"in the tags for all files at once."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu seznama lahko izberete več datotek in uredite eno ali več polj v "
"oznakah za vse datoteke hkrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use &Shift; and the &LMB; to select a contiguous list of files, and &Ctrl; "
"and &LMB; to select individual non-contiguous files."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite &Shift; in &LMB; za izbiro sosednjega seznama datotek in &Ctrl; in "
"&LMB; za izbiro posameznih nesosednjih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the tag editor is not visible, you can enable it by choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag Editor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The tag editor displays in the bottom of the list "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Če urejevalnik oznak ni viden, ga lahko omogočite tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži urejevalnik oznak</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Urejevalnik oznak se prikaže na dnu pogleda "
"seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tag editor behaves slightly differently when you have selected multiple "
"files."
msgstr "Urejevalnik oznak se obnaša nekoliko drugače, ko izberete več datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each field in the tag editor will now show an <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> "
"check box next to it. Any field that has exactly the same contents for all "
"the files you selected, displays that content, and is enabled for editing, "
"with the <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> check box checked."
msgstr ""
"Poleg vsakega polja v urejevalniku oznak bo prikazano potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Omogoči</guilabel>. Vsako polje, ki ima popolnoma enako vsebino za "
"vse datoteke, ki ste jih izbrali, prikaže to vsebino in je omogočeno za "
"urejanje s potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Omogoči</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any field that does not have matching contents in all selected files is not "
"initially editable, and does not display any contents at all."
msgstr ""
"Nobenega polja, ki nima ujemajoče se vsebine v vseh izbranih datotekah, "
"sprva ni mogoče urejati in ne prikaže nobene vsebine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the content of any field, check the <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> "
"check box if it is not already checked, and edit the field as you normally "
"would."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti vsebino katerega koli polja, označite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Omogoči</guilabel>, če še ni potrjeno, in uredite polje kot "
"običajno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done, &LMB; click back in the list view and you will be "
"prompted to save your changes. The prompt dialog will show you a list of the "
"affected files, so you have a chance to check that you are indeed altering "
"the files you intended to."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate, &LMB; kliknite nazaj v pogledu seznama in pozvani boste, da "
"shranite spremembe. Pozivno pogovorno okno vam bo pokazalo seznam prizadetih "
"datotek, tako da boste imeli možnost preveriti, ali res spreminjate "
"datoteke, ki ste jih nameravali."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Rename File dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogovorno okno Preimenuj datoteko</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Rename File dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno Preimenuj datoteko</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Rename File dialog."
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna Preimenuj datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The File Renamer Configuration dialog box is used to configure the Rename "
"File action, which renames a song's based on the information contained "
"within its metadata tags."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija preimenovanja datotek se uporablja za "
"konfiguracijo dejanja Preimenuj datoteko, ki preimenuje skladbo na podlagi "
"informacij, ki jih vsebujejo njene metapodatkovne oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The whole Rename File feature is used to get consistent file names for your "
"music collection (including moving the files if necessary). For example you "
"may have some songs which appear on disk as <filename>01 - Title.mp3</"
"filename> if you got them from <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon</"
"ulink>, while songs from <ulink url=\"http://ocremix.org/\">OCRemix</ulink> "
"might be <filename>Ailsean- Mega_Man_3_Mega_Fire_(OC_Remix).mp3</filename> "
"or something along those lines."
msgstr ""
"Celotna funkcija Preimenuj datoteko se uporablja za pridobitev skladnih imen "
"datotek za vašo glasbeno zbirko (vključno s premikanjem datotek, če je "
"potrebno). Morda imate na primer nekaj pesmi, ki so na disku prikazane kot "
"<filename>01 - Title.mp3</filename>, če ste jih dobili od <ulink url="
"\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon</ulink>, medtem ko pesmi iz <ulink url=\"http://"
"ocremix.org/\">OCRemix</ulink> so lahko <filename>Ailsean- "
"Mega_Man_3_Mega_Fire_(OC_Remix).mp3</filename> ali kaj podobnega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the file renamer allows &juk; to rename those songs to something "
"<quote>sane</quote> on-disk, such as <filename>Ailsean - Mega Fire.mp3</"
"filename> and <filename>The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</filename>. You can even "
"include paths throughout to automatically sort the music (&eg; by year or "
"album), like <filename>$HOME/Music/2003/The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba preimenovanja datotek omogoča &juk; da te pesmi preimenujete v nekaj "
"<quote>razumnega</quote> na disku, kot sta <filename>Ailsean - Mega Fire."
"mp3</filename> in <filename>The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</filename>. Vključite "
"lahko celo poti za samodejno razvrščanje glasbe (&eg;. po letu ali albumu), "
"na primer <filename>$HOME/Music/2003/The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Doing this is as simple as activating the <quote>Rename File</quote> action, "
"either from the <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu> menu, or right-clicking on the "
"files. The default is the <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> "
"shortcut. But before this is done you should setup how the files are to be "
"renamed."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako preprosto, kot da aktivirate dejanje <quote>Preimenuj "
"datoteko</quote> bodisi v meniju <guimenu>Označevalnik</guimenu> ali z "
"desnim klikom na datoteke. Privzeta je bližnjica <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Toda preden to storite, morate nastaviti, kako bodo "
"datoteke preimenovane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That is done from the above mentioned dialog that can be opened with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Renamer...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. You can define a destination path, by "
"using a base music folder and then adding pieces to there. These path pieces "
"would be based on the music metadata such as song title, artist, &etc;, and "
"are added using the <guilabel>Add Category</guilabel> selector."
msgstr ""
"To storite v zgoraj omenjenem pogovornem oknu, ki ga lahko odprete z "
"menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenovanje datotek...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Določite lahko ciljno pot z uporabo osnovne glasbene mape in vanjo nato "
"dodate skladbe. Ti deli poti bi temeljili na glasbenih metapodatkih, kot so "
"naslov pesmi, izvajalec &etc; in bi bili dodani z izbirnikom <guilabel>Dodaj "
"kategorijo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each \"path piece\" has a check box between it allowing a folder separator "
"to be added."
msgstr ""
"Med vsakim \"kosom poti\" je potrditveno polje, ki omogoča dodajanje ločila "
"map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options for each piece, which simply control what happens if the "
"appropriate metadata is empty, and allow a prefix/suffix when the entry is "
"substituted in, can help you to make the renaming procedure more effective."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti za vsak del, ki preprosto nadzirajo, kaj se zgodi, če so ustrezni "
"metapodatki prazni, in dovoljujejo predpono/pripono, ko je vnos zamenjan, "
"vam lahko pomagajo narediti postopek preimenovanja učinkovitejši."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo uganjevalnika oznak</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo uganjevalnika oznak</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Tag Guesser Configuration dialog."
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna konfiguracije uganjevalnika oznak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog is used to configure the "
"<guilabel>Guess from File Name</guilabel> action."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija uganjevalnika oznak se uporablja za "
"konfiguracijo dejanja <guilabel>Ugani iz imena datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog you will see a list on the left of different filename scheme "
"patterns. &juk; includes an extensive set of defaults patterns to match most "
"common filenaming styles. If you'd like to add a new scheme, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> button, and type in your scheme and click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu boste na levi strani videli seznam različnih vzorcev sheme "
"imen datotek. &juk; vključuje obsežen nabor privzetih vzorcev, ki ustrezajo "
"najpogostejšim slogom poimenovanja datotek. Če želite dodati novo shemo, "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>, vnesite svojo shemo in kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can see the currently configured file name schemes which the tag "
"editor uses to extract tag information from a file name. Each string may "
"contain one of the following placeholders:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj si lahko ogledate trenutno konfigurirane sheme imen datotek, ki jih "
"urejevalnik oznak uporablja za pridobivanje informacij o oznaki iz imena "
"datoteke. Vsak niz lahko vsebuje eno od naslednjih rubrik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid "%t: Title"
msgstr "%t: naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "%A: Album"
msgstr "%A: Album"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "%a: Artist"
msgstr "%a: Umetnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "%T: Track"
msgstr "%T: Skladba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "%c: Comment"
msgstr "%c: Komentar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, the file name scheme <quote>[%T] %a - %t</quote> would match "
"<quote>[01] Deep Purple - Smoke on the water</quote> but not <quote>(Deep "
"Purple) Smoke on the water</quote>. For that second name, you would use the "
"scheme <quote>(%a) %t</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, shema imena datoteke <quote>[%T] %a - %t</quote> bi se ujemala z "
"<quote>[01] Deep Purple - Smoke on the water</quote>, ne pa tudi "
"<quote>(Deep Purple) Smoke on the water</quote>. Za to drugo ime bi "
"uporabili shemo <quote>(%a) %t</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try the schemes you have listed one at a time, starting at the "
"top of the list. The first scheme which results in a match will be the "
"scheme used to guess the song's tags. Some songs may match more than one "
"scheme. You can make sure that the correct scheme matches first by selecting "
"the scheme in the list box and then using the arrow buttons to move it to "
"the top of the list."
msgstr ""
"&juk; bo preizkusil sheme, ki ste jih navedli, eno za drugo, začenši na vrhu "
"seznama. Prva shema, ki se bo ujemala, bo shema, uporabljena za ugibanje "
"oznak pesmi. Nekatere pesmi se lahko ujemajo z več kot eno shemo. Najprej se "
"lahko prepričate, da se pravilna shema ujema tako, da izberete shemo v polju "
"s seznamom in jo nato s puščičnimi gumbi premaknete na vrh seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also edit or remove a scheme from the list. Just select the scheme "
"in the list, and use the <guibutton>Modify</guibutton> button to change the "
"scheme, or the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button to remove the scheme "
"from the list."
msgstr ""
"Shemo lahko tudi uredite ali odstranite s seznama. Samo izberite shemo na "
"seznamu in uporabite gumb <guibutton>Spremeni</guibutton>, da spremenite "
"shemo, ali gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>, da odstranite shemo s "
"seznama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Advanced Search dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogovorno okno za napredno iskanje</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Advanced Search dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za napredno iskanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Advanced Search Dialog."
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna naprednega iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Advanced Search dialog is used to create <link linkend=\"juk-search-"
"playlists\">Search Playlists</link>. It allows you to make a fine-grained "
"search among the different tags of your song collection."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Napredno iskanje se uporablja za ustvarjanje <link linkend="
"\"juk-search-playlists\">Iskanja seznamov predvajanja</link>. Omogoča vam "
"natančno iskanje med različnimi oznakami vaše zbirke skladb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of the dialog, you can type in the name of your search playlist. "
"Then, you can define your search criteria in the <guilabel>Search Criteria</"
"guilabel> group."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu pogovornega okna lahko vnesete ime iskalnega seznama predvajanja. "
"Nato lahko določite svoje iskalne kriterije v skupini <guilabel>Iskalni "
"kriteriji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top of the <guilabel>Search Criteria</guilabel> group has two radio "
"buttons, <guilabel>Match any of the following</guilabel> and <guilabel>Match "
"all of the following</guilabel>. If you select <guilabel>Match any of the "
"following</guilabel>, then a match by any of the conditions you define will "
"include the song in the playlist. Otherwise, every condition you define must "
"match in order to include the song in the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu skupine <guilabel>Iskalni kriteriji</guilabel> sta dva izbirna "
"gumba, <guilabel>Ujemanje s katerim koli od naslednjih</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Ujemanje z vsemi naslednjimi</guilabel>. Če izberete "
"<guilabel>Ujemanje s katerim koli od naslednjih</guilabel>, bo ujemanje s "
"katerim koli pogojem, ki ga določite, vključilo pesem na seznam predvajanja. "
"V nasprotnem primeru se mora ujemati vsak pogoj, ki ga določite, da "
"vključite skladbo na seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the radio buttons are the condition definitions. You can add more "
"conditions by using the <guibutton>More</guibutton> button, and remove "
"conditions by using the <guibutton>Fewer</guibutton> button. Any conditions "
"you leave blank are ignored, so you do not have to use <guibutton>Fewer</"
"guibutton> to eliminate empty conditions."
msgstr ""
"Pod izbirnimi gumbi so definicije pogojev. Več pogojev lahko dodate z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Več</guibutton>, pogoje pa odstranite z gumbom <guibutton>Manj</"
"guibutton>. Vsi pogoji, ki jih pustite prazne, so prezrti, zato vam ni treba "
"uporabiti <guibutton>Manj</guibutton>, da odstranite prazne pogoje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every condition definition has three parts: The tag chooser list on the "
"left, the matching style list on the right, and the search text in the "
"middle. The tag chooser lets &juk; know what tag you want to search for the "
"text in. If you choose the special tag \"&lt;All Visible&gt;\", then any tag "
"that you can see in the Collection List listing is fair game to match the "
"search text."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka definicija pogoja ima tri dele: seznam izbirnika oznak na levi, seznam "
"ujemajočih se slogov na desni in iskalno besedilo na sredini. Izbirnik oznak "
"omogoča &juk; veste, v kateri oznaki želite iskati besedilo. Če izberete "
"posebno oznako »&lt;Vse vidno&gt;«, je katera koli oznaka, ki jo lahko "
"vidite na seznamu seznama zbirk, poštena igra, da se ujema z iskalnim "
"besedilom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The match style list lets &juk; know which search method to use. The search "
"methods you can use are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam slogov ujemanja omogoča &juk; vedeti, katero metodo iskanja "
"uporabiti. Metode iskanja, ki jih lahko uporabite, so naslednje:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Matching"
msgstr "Normalno ujemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default matching style. It searches for the given text anywhere "
"in the chosen tag, ignoring case differences. For example a search for mode "
"in the Artist tag would match Depeche Mode."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeti slog ujemanja. Dano besedilo išče kjer koli v izbrani oznaki, "
"ne upošteva pa velikih in malih črk. Iskanje mode v oznaki Artist bi se na "
"primer ujemalo z Depeche Mode."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case Sensitive"
msgstr "Razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This search is just like Normal Matching, except that the search must match "
"the exact case of the text."
msgstr ""
"To iskanje je podobno običajnemu ujemanju, le da se mora iskanje natančno "
"ujemati z velikimi in malimi črkami besedila."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pattern Matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje vzorcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most powerful search method. The search text you type in will "
"define a regular expression used to search within the tag. Regular "
"expressions are beyond the scope of this documentation, but the application "
"&kregexpeditor; can help you form a regular expression. &juk; uses the &Qt; "
"regular expression style."
msgstr ""
"To je najmočnejša metoda iskanja. Iskalno besedilo, ki ga vnesete, bo "
"definiralo regularni izraz, ki se uporablja za iskanje znotraj oznake. "
"Regularni izrazi so izven obsega te dokumentacije, vendar aplikacija "
"&kregexpeditor; vam lahko pomaga oblikovati regularni izraz. &juk; uporablja "
"&Qt; stil regularnega izraza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply choose the conditions you want to include in your search, and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to create your search playlist!"
msgstr ""
"Preprosto izberite pogoje, ki jih želite vključiti v iskanje, in kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da ustvarite iskalni seznam predvajanja!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &juk; Toolbar"
msgstr "&juk; Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Toolbar"
msgstr "Glavna orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &juk; toolbar.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Program &juk; orodna vrstica.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &juk; toolbar.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&juk; orodna vrstica.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The &juk; toolbar.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Program &juk; orodna vrstica.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From left to right in the screenshot above, the icons on the default toolbar "
"are:"
msgstr ""
"Od leve proti desni na zgornjem posnetku zaslona so ikone v privzeti orodni "
"vrstici:"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>New</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Nov</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new playlist. If you hold down the button, a menu will pop up "
"allowing you to select the different kinds of playlists to create."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov seznam predvajanja. Če pridržite gumb, se prikaže meni, v "
"katerem lahko izberete različne vrste seznamov predvajanja, ki jih želite "
"ustvariti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty Playlist..."
msgstr "Prazen seznam predvajanja..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This prompts you for a playlist name, and then inserts it into the Playlist "
"view. The playlist starts out completely empty."
msgstr ""
"To vas pozove k vnosu imena seznama predvajanja in ga nato vstavi v pogled "
"seznama predvajanja. Seznam predvajanja se začne popolnoma prazen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist From Folder..."
msgstr "Seznam predvajanja iz mape..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This prompts you for a folder to open, and then creates a playlist "
"containing the music within the folder and any sub-folders. The name of the "
"created playlist is the same as the name of the selected folder."
msgstr ""
"To vas pozove, da odprete mapo, nato pa ustvari seznam predvajanja, ki "
"vsebuje glasbo v mapi in morebitnih podmapah. Ime ustvarjenega seznama "
"predvajanja je enako imenu izbrane mape."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Playlist..."
msgstr "Išči seznam predvajanja..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This brings up the Advanced Search Dialog, allowing you to create a "
"<quote>virtual playlist</quote>. Any songs in your Collection List that "
"match the search criteria that you specify in the Advanced Search Dialog "
"will be added to the new playlist. As your Collection List changes, the new "
"playlist will as well. For example, if you create a playlist of all of your "
"Depeche Mode songs, and then add another Depeche Mode song to your "
"Collection List, it will show up in the Depeche Mode playlist with no "
"special action required on your part."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno za napredno iskanje, ki vam omogoča ustvarjanje "
"<quote>virtualnega seznama predvajanja</quote>. Vse pesmi na vašem seznamu "
"zbirk, ki ustrezajo iskalnim kriterijem, ki ste jih določili v pogovornem "
"oknu za napredno iskanje, bodo dodane na nov seznam predvajanja. Ko se "
"spremeni vaš seznam zbirk, se bo spremenil tudi novi seznam predvajanja. Na "
"primer, če ustvarite seznam predvajanja vseh svojih skladb skupine Depeche "
"Mode in nato na svoj seznam zbirke dodate še eno pesem skupine Depeche Mode, "
"se bo prikazala na seznamu predvajanja skupine Depeche Mode, ne da bi morali "
"ukrepati."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Odpri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a file to the collection list (if it's active) or to the currently "
"selected playlist. Adding a file to a playlist will add it to the collection "
"list automatically, but not vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj datoteko na seznam zbirk (če je aktiven) ali na trenutno izbrani "
"seznam predvajanja. Če dodate datoteko na seznam predvajanja, jo boste "
"samodejno dodali na seznam zbirk, ne pa obratno."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Shrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the currently selected playlist. To save a tag you have edited, either "
"select another item, or press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo> instead."
msgstr ""
"Shrani trenutno izbrani seznam predvajanja. Če želite shraniti oznako, ki "
"ste jo uredili, izberite drug element ali namesto tega pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Cut</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Izreži</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a playlist or song is selected, cut (remove) it from the list. If the tag "
"editor is active, this works like cut in any editor, removing the selected "
"text, but keeping a copy on the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbran seznam predvajanja ali skladba, jo izreže (odstrani) s seznama. "
"Če je urejevalnik oznak aktiven, to deluje kot izrez v katerem koli "
"urejevalniku, pri čemer se odstrani izbrano besedilo, vendar ostane kopija v "
"odložišču."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Copy</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Kopiraj</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the tag editor is active, this works like copy in any editor, placing a "
"copy of the selected text on the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Če je urejevalnik oznak aktiven, to deluje kot kopiranje v katerem koli "
"urejevalniku, pri čemer se kopija izbranega besedila postavi v odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use copy on a song in the collection list, the url is placed on the "
"clipboard, so you can paste it. For example, you could paste the url into a "
"text editor, &konqueror;, or another playlist."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabite kopiranje pesmi na seznamu zbirk, se url postavi v odložišče, "
"tako da ga lahko prilepite. Na primer, URL lahko prilepite v urejevalnik "
"besedila, &konqueror; ali drug seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Paste</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Prilepi</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you previously either cut or copied a url from the collection list, you "
"can paste the url back into a new playlist. You could also paste a url you "
"have copied from &konqueror; or any other application. If you are operating "
"in the tag editor, paste will paste any text currently on the clipboard into "
"the selected field."
msgstr ""
"Če ste predhodno bodisi izrezali ali kopirali URL s seznama zbirke, lahko "
"URL prilepite nazaj na nov seznam predvajanja. Lahko tudi prilepite url, ki "
"ste ga kopirali iz &konqueror; ali katero koli drugo aplikacijo. Če "
"uporabljate urejevalnik oznak, bo paste v izbrano polje prilepila katero "
"koli besedilo, ki je trenutno v odložišču."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Search Bar"
msgstr "Pokaži vrstico za iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide <link linkend=\"search-bar\">the search bar</link>."
msgstr "Pokaži ali skrij <link linkend=\"search-bar\">iskalno vrstico</link>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Tag Editor"
msgstr "Pokaži urejevalnik oznak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show or hide <link linkend=\"tagging-a-single-file\">the tag editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži ali skrij <link linkend=\"tagging-a-single-file\">urejevalnik oznak</"
"link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play controls"
msgstr "Kontrole predvajanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These work like any standard media player you may have come across. The "
"controls are <guiicon>Play</guiicon>, <guiicon>Pause</guiicon>, "
"<guiicon>Stop</guiicon>, <guiicon>Previous </guiicon> and <guiicon>Next</"
"guiicon>."
msgstr ""
"Ti delujejo kot kateri koli standardni medijski predvajalnik, ki ste ga "
"morda srečali. Kontrolniki so <guiicon>Predvajaj</guiicon>, <guiicon>Premor</"
"guiicon>, <guiicon>Ustavi</guiicon>, <guiicon>Prejšnja</guiicon> in "
"<guiicon>Naslednja</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a tracking bar, showing how far along (relatively) in the "
"current song you are. You can drag this slider with the mouse in order to "
"skip forwards or backwards within a track."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja tudi vrstica za sledenje, ki prikazuje, kako daleč ste (relativno) v "
"trenutni pesmi. Ta drsnik lahko povlečete z miško, da preskočite naprej ali "
"nazaj znotraj skladbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally there is a volume slider. As you may expect, this raises and lowers "
"the volume. <quote>Loud</quote> is on the right, and <quote>Quiet</quote> is "
"on the left."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu je tu še drsnik za glasnost. Kot lahko pričakujete, to poveča in "
"zmanjša glasnost. <quote>Glasno</quote> je na desni, <quote>Tiho</quote> pa "
"na levi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1009
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Search bar"
msgstr "Iskalna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search bar allows you to quickly search for a song in the collection "
"list or a playlist."
msgstr ""
"Iskalna vrstica vam omogoča hitro iskanje pesmi na seznamu zbirk ali seznamu "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply typing text into the search bar will reduce the visible list of songs "
"to those which contain that text in any visible column. Pressing &Enter; "
"will start playing the top match in the playlist view."
msgstr ""
"Enostavno vnašanje besedila v iskalno vrstico bo zmanjšalo vidni seznam "
"skladb na tiste, ki to besedilo vsebujejo v katerem koli vidnem stolpcu. S "
"pritiskom &Enter; bo začel predvajati najvišje ujemanje v pogledu seznama "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching begins instantly when text is entered into the search field. "
"Searching is incremental, that is, as you type each character into the text "
"field, the search is narrowed further. This is useful to find a song where "
"you only remember part of a name, for instance."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje se začne takoj, ko v iskalno polje vnesete besedilo. Iskanje je "
"postopoma, kar pomeni, da se iskanje dodatno zoži, ko vnesete vsak znak v "
"besedilno polje. To je uporabno, če na primer najdete pesem, pri kateri se "
"spomnite samo dela imena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu and Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenčni meni in ukazi"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Meniji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Empty Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nov</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Prazen seznam predvajanja...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new playlist"
msgstr "Ustvari nov seznam predvajanja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nov</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Išči seznam predvajanja...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new <link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\">search playlist</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov <link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\">seznam predvajanja za "
"iskanje</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Playlist From Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Seznam predvajanja iz Mapa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new playlist, containing all music files in a folder and any sub-"
"folders. Any music within playlists files that &juk; recognizes will also be "
"added."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov seznam predvajanja, ki vsebuje vse glasbene datoteke v mapi in "
"morebitnih podmapah. Vsaka glasba v datotekah seznamov predvajanja, ki jih "
"&juk; prepozna, bo tudi dodana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file (or files) to add to the collection list. If you select a "
"playlist file, every file in the playlist will be added."
msgstr ""
"Izberite datoteko (ali datoteke), ki jo želite dodati na seznam zbirk. Če "
"izberete datoteko seznama predvajanja, bodo dodane vse datoteke na seznamu "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje map...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens the same window that is shown on a first &juk; start"
msgstr ""
"Ta menijski element odpre isto okno, kot je prikazano pri prvem zagonu &juk;a"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a folder (or folders) to add to the collection list. These folders "
"will also be rescanned whenever &juk; is started or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> is chosen."
msgstr ""
"Izberite mapo (ali mape), ki jo želite dodati na seznam zbirk. Te mape bodo "
"prav tako ponovno pregledane, kadar &juk; se zažene ali pa je izbrana "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Znova naloži</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select folders that should not be automatically searched (which "
"would override the list of folders to scan on startup). This way you can "
"avoid having to completely change up your music layout on-disk just to keep "
"&juk; from automatically grabbing songs you do not want or need managed from "
"within &juk;."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi mape, ki jih ne bi smeli samodejno preiskati (kar bi "
"preglasilo seznam map za prečesavanje ob zagonu). Tako se lahko izognete "
"temu, da bi morali popolnoma spremeniti postavitev glasbe na disku samo "
"zato, da &juk; od samodejnega zajemanja skladb, ki jih ne želite ali "
"potrebujete, da jih upravljate znotraj &juk;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Manage Folders dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Upravljanje map"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Manage Folders Dialog."
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za upravljanje map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove files that are already in the collection list, you can "
"enable the <guilabel>File Name (full path)</guilabel> column in a playlist "
"and then use the search bar to find the offending path name, select and "
"remove the files that are shown."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti datoteke, ki so že na seznamu zbirk, lahko omogočite "
"stolpec <guilabel>Ime datoteke (celotna pot)</guilabel> na seznamu "
"predvajanja in nato uporabite iskalno vrstico, da poiščete napačno ime poti, "
"izberete in odstranite prikazane datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename a playlist."
msgstr "Preimenuj seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Duplicate...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dvojnik...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a duplicate of the selected playlist, and prompt for a new name."
msgstr "Ustvari dvojnik izbranega seznama predvajanja in zahteva novo ime."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the tag information on every file in the selected playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži informacije o oznaki za vsako datoteko na izbranem seznamu "
"predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the selected playlist."
msgstr "Odstrani izbrani seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist."
msgstr "Shrani izbrani seznam predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist, with a different name."
msgstr "Shrani izbrani seznam predvajanja z drugim imenom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Uredi"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Počisti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected songs from the playlist."
msgstr "Odstrani izbrane pesmi s seznama predvajanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogleda"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Search Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži iskalno vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"search-"
"bar\">Search Bar</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopno dejanje, ki nastavi, ali je <link linkend=\"search-bar"
"\">Iskalna vrstica</link> prikazana ali ne."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag Editor</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži urejevalnik oznak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <interface>Tag Editor</"
"interface> is shown."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopno dejanje, ki nastavi, ali je <interface>Urejevalnik oznak</"
"interface> prikazan ali ne."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži zgodovino</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"juk-"
"history-playlists\">History Playlist</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopno dejanje, ki nastavi, ali je <link linkend=\"juk-history-"
"playlists\">Seznam predvajanja zgodovine</link> prikazan ali ne."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Privzeto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\">Default View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi na <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\">privzeti način pogleda</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Kompaktno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\">Compact View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi v <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\">način kompaktnega pogleda</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Tree</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Drevo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\">Tree View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi v <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\">način drevesnega pogleda</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player Menu"
msgstr "Meni predvajalnika"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Random Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naključno predvajanje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Random Play setting. If Random "
"Play is enabled, then &juk; will randomly select a random song from the "
"current playlist when the currently playing song is over."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopna možnost, ki nadzoruje nastavitev naključnega predvajanja. Če "
"je omogočeno naključno predvajanje, potem &juk; bo naključno izbral "
"naključno skladbo s trenutnega seznama predvajanja, ko je trenutno "
"predvajana skladba končana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Loop Playlist</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zanka seznama predvajanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Loop Playlist setting. If Loop "
"Playlist is enabled, then &juk; will start playing from the beginning when "
"it has finished playing every song in the current playlist."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopna možnost, ki nadzoruje nastavitev zanke seznama predvajanja. "
"Če je zanka omogočena, potem bo  &juk; začel predvajati spet od začetka, ko "
"bo končal predvajanje vseh pesmi na trenutnem seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predvajaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command starts playing the currently selected song, or resumes playback "
"of the song if it was paused."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz začne predvajati trenutno izbrano skladbo ali nadaljuje predvajanje "
"skladbe, če je bila začasno ustavljena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command pauses the currently playing song. Use the Play command to "
"restart playback."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz začasno ustavi trenutno predvajano skladbo. Za ponovni zagon "
"predvajanja uporabite ukaz Predvajaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command stops the playback of the currently playing song. You cannot "
"resume playback from its current position after that."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz ustavi predvajanje trenutno predvajane pesmi. Po tem ne morete "
"nadaljevati predvajanja s trenutnega položaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command skips to the next song to play in the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz preskoči na naslednjo skladbo za predvajanje na seznamu predvajanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Predvajalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command plays the song that was playing before the currently playing "
"song."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz predvaja skladbo, ki se je predvajala pred trenutno predvajano "
"skladbo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagger Menu"
msgstr "Meni za označevanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Označi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command saves any changes to the tags that you are editing. Normally, "
"changes are not saved until you deselect the file you are editing."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz shrani vse spremembe oznak, ki jih urejate. Običajno se spremembe ne "
"shranijo, dokler ne prekličete izbire datoteke, ki jo urejate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Oznaka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the currently selected files from the Collection List "
"and any playlists containing it, and then deletes the selected file from the "
"disk."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz izbriše trenutno izbrane datoteke s seznama zbirke in vseh seznamov "
"predvajanja, ki jih vsebujejo, nato pa izbriše izbrano datoteko z diska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Označevalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Osveži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command allows you to refresh playlist tags after changing them."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz vam omogoča, da osvežite oznake seznama predvajanja, potem ko jih "
"spremenite."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Filename</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Označevalnik</guimenu><guisubmenu>Informacije o "
"uganjevalniku oznak</guisubmenu><guimenuitem> Iz imena datoteke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by scanning the "
"filename. You can configure the patterns used for guessing by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which opens the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-"
"configuration\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz poskuša uganiti oznake izbranih datotek s prečesavanjem imena "
"datoteke. Vzorce, ki se uporabljajo za ugibanje, lahko konfigurirate tako, "
"da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Uganjevalnik oznak...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki odpre "
"<link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration\">Pogovorno okno za "
"konfiguracijo uganjevalnika oznak</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Internet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Označevalnik</guimenu><guisubmenu>Informacije o oznaki "
"uganjevalnika</guisubmenu><guimenuitem> Iz interneta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by using the "
"<application>TunePimp</application> library provided with <ulink url="
"\"http://www.musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz poskuša uganiti oznake izbranih datotek z uporabo knjižnice "
"<application>TunePimp</application>, ki je priložena <ulink url=\"http://www."
"musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rename File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Označevalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenuj datoteko</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command allows you to rename a file or a group of files for the "
"selected songs in the playlist. Before the real rename happens &juk; will "
"show a preview dialog where you can confirm or cancel the action."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz vam omogoča preimenovanje datoteke ali skupine datotek za izbrane "
"pesmi na seznamu predvajanja. Preden se zgodi pravo preimenovanje &juk; "
"prikaže pogovorno okno za predogled, kjer lahko potrdite ali prekličete "
"dejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files will be renamed according to the parameters defined using <link "
"linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">Rename File dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke bodo preimenovane v skladu s parametri, določenimi z <link linkend="
"\"juk-rename-dialog\">pogovornim oknom Preimenuj datoteko</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Main / Play Toolbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikazane orodne vrstice</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Glavna orodna vrstica / predvajanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands show or hide the <link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Main Toolbar</"
"link> and the <link linkend=\"play-toolbar\">Play Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ti ukazi prikažejo ali skrijejo <link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Glavno orodno "
"vrstico</link> in <link linkend=\"play-toolbar\">Orodno vrstico Predvajaj</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dok v sistemski vrstici</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an icon in your "
"system tray. You can use the system tray icon to tell if &juk; is playing, "
"and control playback."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopna možnost. Če je omogočeno, &juk; prikaže ikono v sistemski "
"vrstici. Z ikono v sistemski vrstici lahko ugotovite, ali &juk; predvaja in "
"upravljajte predvajanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stay in System Tray on Close</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ostani v sistemski vrstici ob "
"zaprtju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will remain running if you close "
"the main window. The <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem> option "
"must also be enabled. To quit &juk;, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> command from the main "
"window, or the <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> command from the system "
"tray's context menu."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopna možnost. Če je omogočeno, &juk; bo še naprej deloval, če "
"zaprete glavno okno. Omogočena mora biti tudi možnost <guimenuitem>Dok na "
"sistemskem pladnju</guimenuitem>. Če želite zapreti &juk;, uporabite ukaz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v glavnem oknu ali ukaz <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem> iz "
"sistema kontekstni meni pladnja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &juk; is started up when it is set to dock in the system tray on startup "
"a simple notification will be shown (as otherwise the user may wonder why "
"&juk; window did not open up). It is possible to remove this additional "
"notification by going to <menuchoice><guimenu>Common Appearance and "
"Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Application and System Notifications</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &systemsettings; to manage <guilabel>JuK music "
"player</guilabel> application notifications. Just uncheck <guilabel>Show a "
"message in a popup</guilabel> item for <guimenuitem>JuK running in dock "
"mode</guimenuitem>. More information on &kde; notification settings can be "
"found <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če &juk; se zažene, ko je nastavljen tako, da zasidra v sistemski vrstici ob "
"zagonu, bo prikazano preprosto obvestilo (ker se sicer lahko uporabnik "
"vpraša, zakaj se okno &juk; ni odprlo). To dodatno obvestilo lahko "
"odstranite tako, da obiščete <menuchoice><guimenu>Skupni videz in vedenje</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obvestila o aplikacijah in sistemu</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v &systemsettings; za upravljanje obvestil aplikacije "
"<guilabel>predvajalnik glasbe JuK</guilabel>. Preprosto počistite polje "
"<guilabel>Pokaži sporočilo v pojavnem oknu</guilabel> za <guimenuitem>JuK, "
"ki teče v priklopnem načinu</guimenuitem>. Več informacij o &kde; nastavitve "
"obvestil najdete <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Popup Track Announcement</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojavno obvestilo o skladbi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an indicator "
"whenever a song starts playing, with information on the artist and title, "
"and with buttons allowing you to quickly switch to a different song. The "
"Dock in System Tray option must also be enabled."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopna možnost. Če je omogočeno, &juk; bo prikazal indikator "
"vsakič, ko se pesem začne predvajati, z informacijami o izvajalcu in naslovu "
"ter z gumbi, ki vam omogočajo hiter preklop na drugo skladbo. Omogočena mora "
"biti tudi možnost Dok na sistemskem pladnju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1526
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uganjevalnik oznak...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration"
"\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the "
"patterns used to guess tag information from filenames."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz odpre <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration\">pogovorno okno "
"Konfiguracija uganjevalnika oznak</link>, kjer lahko spremenite vzorce, ki "
"se uporabljajo za uganjevanje informacij o oznakah iz imen datotek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1538
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>File Renamer...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenovanje datotek...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">File Renamer "
"Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the way &juk; renames "
"files for you."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz odpre <link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">pogovorno okno "
"Konfiguracija preimenovanja datotek</link>, kjer lahko spremenite način "
"&juk; preimenuje datoteke namesto vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &juk; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &juk; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keybinding Reference"
msgstr "Referenca za vezavo tipk"

